  <note line="49" original="anudayaṃ (bahūsu) dvittakāraṇaṃ pana gavesitabbaṃ" reference-line="22" id="5">
    <extra> dvittakāraṇaṃ pana gavesitabbaṃ</extra>
    <alternatives>
      <alternative source-abbr="vri" source="vipassana research institut">anuddayaṃ</alternative>
      <alternative source-abbr="bahūsu" source="bahūsu">anudayaṃ</alternative>
    </alternatives>
    <type>auto</type>
    <previous>. Aho, vata me dhammaṃ suṇeyyuṃ, sutvā ca pana dhammaṃ ājāneyyuṃ, ājānitvā ca pana tathattāya paṭipajjeyyu’nti. Iti dhammasudhammataṃ paṭicca paresaṃ dhammaṃ deseti, kāruññaṃ paṭicca anuddayaṃ </previous>
  </note>
  <note line="58" original="gahapatikāni (sī.)" reference-line="30" id="6">
